    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Staircase units that consist of one tread and one riser, or any similar element providing a horizontal surface on which to support the foot of a person descending or ascending.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
